WEBVTT

00:04.500 --> 00:05.810
Ah, found them!

00:09.580 --> 00:10.700
Gesundhoof.

00:10.850 --> 00:13.000
Why, thank you, Applejack.

00:13.150 --> 00:17.150
I still can't believe
it's been almost 100 moons

00:17.300 --> 00:19.400
since our last
family reunion.

00:19.550 --> 00:22.510
Oh, I remember it
like it was yesterday.

00:22.660 --> 00:26.250
Well, you have been talking about it
pretty much every day since then.

00:26.400 --> 00:29.670
Apple Bloom, how are them
RSVPs coming along?

00:29.820 --> 00:32.270
Who's showing their muzzle
at the reunion?

00:32.420 --> 00:33.580
Everypony!

00:33.730 --> 00:36.780
Everypony?
Feathers on a goat.

00:36.930 --> 00:37.800
Are you sure?

00:37.950 --> 00:40.480
Well, I got RSVPs from

00:40.630 --> 00:42.840
Apples from Yonderhill,
Hollow Shades,

00:42.990 --> 00:44.810
Galloping Gorge,
Foal Mountains,

00:44.960 --> 00:47.640
Apples from Fillydelphia,
Tall Tale Town,

00:47.790 --> 00:49.670
and all the Apples
from Appleloosa.

00:50.690 --> 00:52.620
Oh, and how could I forget?

00:52.770 --> 00:55.230
Manehattan!
Babs is coming.

00:55.380 --> 00:57.510
I get to see my favorite cousin!

00:57.660 --> 01:00.700
I think we're gonna need
a bigger cider trough.

